# Code Style & Quality Rules

## TypeScript Rules

- Strict mode enabled.
- `any` is FORBIDDEN.
- All external data must be validated.
- Zod is mandatory for validation.

## React Rules

- No unnecessary state.
- No prop drilling beyond 2 levels.
- No useEffect unless absolutely required.
- Prefer server actions over client fetches.

## Styling Rules

- Tailwind is utility-first, NOT chaos-first.
- shadcn/ui components must be preferred.
- No inline styles.
- Design tokens > random values.

## Comments

- No obvious comments.
- Comment ONLY complex logic or architectural decisions.

## Error Handling

- All async operations must handle failure.
- Loading, error, empty states are REQUIRED.
